                    "Description" : {
                        "Id" : "outcome_0_0",
                        "Name" : "Virago fired.",
                        "Details" : "\"I don't trust you. And I won't drop with someone I don't trust. You miss your former Clanmates so much, go. Run along and see if they'll take you back. Maybe they'll let you redeem your pathetic honor in a [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[TBoneLoreTouman],<i>solahma</i>]] unit.\"\r\n\r\n[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]]'s expression is stony. She turns and leaves without a word, taking the first shuttle off the <i>Argo</i>. As promised, she left without taking a thing, including a small fortune and a cache of Clan tech. Most of the crew breathes a little easier with her off the ship.",
